Content:
I use Siri and voice dictation every day for:<p><pre><code>    &quot;text my wife I&#x27;m on my way home&quot;
    &quot;set timer for 10 minutes&quot; (cooking)
    &quot;Directions to 101 spear st, san francisco&quot;
    &quot;Remind me to ______ at 5pm today&quot;
</code></pre>
... and  writing meeting summaries in the car.  (always needs some fixing afterwards from my mac)<p>It sucks for lots of other stuff, but I&#x27;ve found these pretty useful.
